<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkey-tax-number-and-residence-address-update">Turkey Tax Number and Residence Address Update</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As a student in Turkey, it is mandatory to obtain a tax number in order to <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-student-bank-account-opening/" data-type="post" data-id="3134">open a bank account</a>, conclude a lease agreement or benefit from certain public services. It is important to update this information after a change of address.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="getting-tax-number-for-international-students-in-turkey">Getting Tax Number for International Students in Turkey</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To obtain a tax number, simply go to the nearest Tax Office and present your passport and proof of residence. You should also update your address information during the process. If you have changed your address, registering your current address with the tax office will prevent future problems with banks and other official institutions.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The process of getting a tax number is free and usually takes 10-15 minutes. You can check your information after an address change in our article Getting a Tax Number for International Students in Turkey.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="lease-agreement-or-dormitory-documents">Lease Agreement or Dormitory Documents</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkey, you will usually be asked for your new lease agreement or an official letter from the dormitory management to prove your change of address. These documents must have your full name, surname and new address written on them.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-to-consider-after-address-change">What to Consider After Address Change</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="bank-and-university-transactions-with-your-new-address">Bank and University Transactions with Your New Address</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Notifying your new address to your bank is very important for the security of your bank accounts and for official correspondence to reach the correct address. Also be sure to submit your new address details to your university&#8217;s student affairs office. This ensures that your university letters or documents reach the correct address.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="transport-and-health-insurance-information">Transport and Health Insurance Information</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you have a <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-toplu-tasima-kullanimi/" data-type="post" data-id="7248">public transportation card</a> (Istanbulkart, Ankarakart, etc.), you need to enter your address into the system after you change your address. For health insurance (SSI or private insurance), reporting your change of address ensures that your insurance policy is kept up to date.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="haydi-step-into-the-dream-of-education-in-turkey">Haydi, Step into the Dream of Education in Turkey!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The system is very practical and supportive for foreign students who want to study in Turkey. If you prepare your documents completely and apply to the right institutions, you can formalize your new address in a short time.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Come now to <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">RoadToStudy</a> to learn about the application process and continue your studies in Turkey with peace of mind.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-to-change-address-for-foreign-contacts">How to change address for foreign contacts</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">A change of address must be reported in person at the Migration Management Authority or the civil registry office.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-to-change-address-for-a-student">How to change address for a student</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Foreign students must update their new address within 20 days by going to the Immigration Administration.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-to-register-the-address-of-foreigners-in-2025">How to register the address of foreigners in 2025?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Foreigners who obtain a residence permit can register their address at the population directorate or via e-Government.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="whose-number-is-157">Whose number is 157?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">157 is the General Directorate of Migration Management&#8217;s counseling and information line for foreigners.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-10-22T10:20:32Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:50:12Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/change-of-address-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Change of Address in Turkey: A Guide for Foreign Students","title":"change-of-address-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'change-of-address-in-turkey' );
