<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Take action now and secure your student life in Turkey by getting your foreign identity card!</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-an-international-student-id-card">What is an international student ID card?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The International Student Identity Card (ISIC) is the only document that proves your student status internationally and provides thousands of discounts and benefits worldwide.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-an-international-student-card">What is an international student card?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The &#8220;International Student Card&#8221; (ISIC) is an official student ID that provides students with global discounts and services for travel, accommodation, museums, transportation and more.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-to-get-an-isic-card">How to get an ISIC card</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The ISIC card can usually be obtained through authorized agencies, some student organizations or the official ISIC Turkey website by applying with a valid student document, a photocopy of ID/passport and a photograph.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">Can foreign students studying in Turkey obtain Turkish citizenship?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Studying in Turkey does not give <strong>direct</strong> citizenship rights; however, foreign students who fulfill the general requirements with uninterrupted and legal residence period (student residence does not count) can apply for citizenship in the future through <strong>general means</strong>.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-10-31T08:38:03Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:49:40Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/identity-card-for-international-students.webp","alt":"Identity Card for International Students in Turkey","title":"identity-card-for-international-students"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'identity-card-for-international-students' );
