<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-does-the-code-v164-mean">What does the code V164 mean?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">V-164 is an important entry ban/restriction code. The cause is usually related to a serious breach of security, order or health/law. Abolition is possible, but it requires a process and there is no guarantee of success in all cases.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-10-28T08:48:46Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:49:51Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'grounds-for-deportation-and-legal-rights' );
