<iframe loading="lazy" title="Bir Bölüm Üç Açı - İşletme Mezun &amp; Öğrenci" width="720" height="405" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/r2IZK4-joDM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozyegin-university-faculty-of-business-administration">Özyegin University Faculty of Business Administration</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-universitesi-isletme-fakultesi/">Özyeğin University School of Business</a> stands out with its modern campus facilities, innovative education programs and strong academic staff. The university&#8217;s Çekmeköy Campus offers students not only an academic but also a socially rich university experience with its social living areas, large green areas and modern classrooms.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The main objective of Ozyegin University&#8217;s Business Administration Undergraduate Program is to provide students with a management vision that blends the needs of today with the rising values of tomorrow. This vision aims to train management candidates and entrepreneurs who can assume a leadership role in the business world.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="education-fees-and-scholarship-opportunities">Education Fees and Scholarship Opportunities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The annual tuition fee for Özyeğin University&#8217;s Business Administration Department for the 2025-2026 academic year is set at <strong>$22,000</strong>. However, the university helps students to cover this fee more easily through merit scholarships.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="2025-2026-academic-year-fees">2025-2026 Academic Year Fees</h4>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Scholarship Rate</th>
<th>Discounted Fee</th>
<th>Prepayment</th>
<th>1st Installment (Fall)</th>
<th>2. Installment (Spring)</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>50%</td>
<td>$11,000</td>
<td>$1,000</td>
<td>$4,500</td>
<td>$5,500</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">All prospective students are automatically considered for scholarships at the time of application. In addition, criteria such as diploma grades, national and international exam results, certificates and reference letters also affect scholarship rates.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="success-scholarships-and-discounts">Success Scholarships and Discounts</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University offers scholarships to students in order to motivate them and reward success. Thanks to these scholarships, students can continue their education by gaining both cost advantage and motivation for academic success.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozyegin-university-business-administration-undergraduate-programs-goal-and-vision">Ozyegin University Business Administration Undergraduate Program&#8217;s Goal and Vision</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Business Administration Undergraduate Program aims to provide students with up-to-date business knowledge through a modern curriculum, while also developing leadership and entrepreneurial skills. The program aims for students to become graduates who are ready for the business world and have the competencies needed by the sectors.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="aacsb-accreditation-and-quality-assurance">AACSB Accreditation and Quality Assurance</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University School of Business is in the process of AACSB accreditation. This accreditation is one of the most prestigious certificates certifying the quality of education of business schools at the international level. In this way, students receive a quality education and the advantage of a globally recognized diploma.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more information about the details in this section, please see <a href="https://www.ozyegin.edu.tr/tr/isletme/hakkinda" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ozyegin University Business Administration Program page</a>.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="specialized-areas-in-the-business-administration-undergraduate-program">Specialized Areas in the Business Administration Undergraduate Program</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In the Business Administration Undergraduate Program, students can specialize in specific areas according to their career goals and graduate better prepared for the industry. Specialized areas offered at Özyeğin University Department of Business Administration include:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Specialized Fields</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Marketing</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Finance</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Operations Management</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Management</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Management Information Systems</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</tbody>
</table>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students who reach 90 ECTS and above credits in these fields can declare this field in the diploma supplement by completing 4 in-program/field elective courses (24 ECTS). However, the choice of field is not compulsory; students who wish can continue their graduation path as &#8220;General Business Administration&#8221;.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="marketing-finance-and-management-information-systems">Marketing, Finance and Management Information Systems</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For example, a student who wants to specialize in marketing can gain in-depth knowledge on brand management, consumer behavior and digital marketing. In the field of finance, investment, financial analysis and risk management courses can make a difference in the financial sectors after graduation. Management Information Systems makes it possible to take part in digital transformation projects by bringing technology and business together.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="field-choice-and-diploma-effects">Field Choice and Diploma Effects</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This specialization is added to the diplomas of students who choose a field of study, which helps graduates stand out in the sector. Thus, students can not only get a broad business education, but also gain deep knowledge of the sector they are interested in and be one step ahead in their job applications.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="sectoral-solutions-and-real-business-projects">Sectoral Solutions and Real Business Projects</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University&#8217;s Business Administration Program is committed to providing students with not only theoretical knowledge but also experience in the industry. In Sectoral Solutions courses, guest speakers from the business world, company and factory visits and case studies are conducted. In this way, students have the opportunity to apply what they learn in the classroom to the real world.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="courses-and-company-collaborations">Courses and Company Collaborations</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In the final year, students take part in real business projects in collaboration with companies from different sectors. Thanks to these projects, students develop skills such as leadership, teamwork and problem solving and are equipped to adapt to the sector immediately after graduation.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="graduation-requirements-and-internship-process">Graduation Requirements and Internship Process</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For graduation, students must complete a total of 44 courses and a compulsory internship program of at least 8 weeks. Graduation requirements in table:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th><strong>Course Type</strong></th><th><strong>Number</strong></th><th><strong>ECTS</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>BABUS Core Courses</td><td>32</td><td>164</td></tr><tr><td>BABUS In-Program / Major Electives</td><td>4</td><td>24</td></tr><tr><td>In-Faculty Electives</td><td>4</td><td>24</td></tr><tr><td>Out-of-Faculty Electives</td><td>2</td><td>12</td></tr><tr><td>Free Electives</td><td>2</td><td>12</td></tr><tr><td>Internship / Certificate</td><td>–</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Total</strong></td><td><strong>44</strong></td><td><strong>240</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="career-and-sectoral-opportunities-in-business">Career and Sectoral Opportunities in Business</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ozyeğin University Department of Business Administration students have the chance to make a strong start in different sectors of the business world. There are open doors for graduates in many sectors such as consumer goods, industrial products, energy, financial services, health, social services, retail, tourism, hospitality and entertainment.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="target-sectors-and-potential-business-areas">Target Sectors and Potential Business Areas</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university allows students to specialize in different sectors and helps graduates choose the career path that best suits them. For example, a student specializing in quality management in health can more easily access managerial positions in hospitals, while a student focusing on finance increases the chances of finding a job in the banking or investment sector.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="graduation-with-strong-academic-foundations">Graduation with Strong Academic Foundations</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The theoretical and practical courses offered by Ozyegin University enable students to take firm steps into the business world after graduation. Real projects, case studies and experiences intertwined with the sector make it easier for graduates to gain sectoral awareness and stand out in their careers.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="now-at-ozyegin-business-administration-step-into-your-dream-career">Now at Özyeğin Business School: Take a step toward your dream career!</h2>


<p>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To join the leaders of the future and become one of the most sought-after graduates of the sectors, Özyeğin University Faculty of Business Administration is waiting for you! Apply now to take your place in this program full of modern campus, quality academic staff and sectoral opportunities!</p>



