<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarships-and-fees-how-much">Scholarships and Fees: How Much?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">One of the most critical issues for many of us: scholarships and fees. <strong>Özyeğin University Department of Economics</strong> stands out with different scholarship and discount opportunities. Özyeğin University, as one of Turkey&#8217;s top scholarship awarding universities, conducts a comprehensive scholarship evaluation every year. All applicants are included in this evaluation without a separate process for the scholarship application.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The annual tuition fee is determined by the Board of Trustees and is paid in two installments. Payment dates and details are announced in the university&#8217;s Academic Calendar. English Preparatory Education fee is the same as the program fees.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozyegin-university-economics-fees-for-2025-2026">Ozyegin University Economics Fees for 2025-2026</h3>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
