<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Studying at the Department of Economics at Ozyegin University means not only gaining theoretical knowledge, but also becoming a competitive professional in the global economic world. Quotas for the 2025-2026 academic year are limited and competition is high. Take advantage by investing in your future today. Apply now and take the step that will make a difference in the economy! </p>



