<iframe loading="lazy" title="Bir Bölüm Üç Açı - Ekonomi Mezun &amp; Öğrenci" width="720" height="405" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GiIrT1y7pSQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In today&#8217;s world where globalization is in full swing, it is becoming more and more important to understand how individuals, companies and markets work, and to develop strategies by analyzing the economic balances of countries.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>The main goal of the Department of Economics at Ozyegin University</strong> is to provide students with a vision to understand and explain the ever-changing economic dynamics that we observe in the business world and on a global scale. In this world of increasing competition between individuals, companies and countries, this program, which combines economic facts with real-life applications, aims to enrich the problem-solving and analytical skills of its graduates and their perspective on life.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><em>Also <strong>Özyeğin University Department of Economics</strong> is in the process of AACSB accreditation.</em></p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="training-duration-and-credits">Training Duration and Credits</h3>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Feature</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Language of instruction</td>
<td>English</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Term</td>
<td>4 years (Preparatory class except)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Total ECTS Credit</td>
<td>240 ECTS</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Compulsory Internship</td>
<td>Minimum 8 weeks (60 working days)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Elective Courses</td>
<td>Finance, business, software, international economics, etc.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="mufredat-ornekleri">Curriculum Examples</h3>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>and 2nd year: Microeconomics, Macroeconomics, Mathematical Methods, Statistics</li>



<li>year: Sectoral Analysis, Data Analysis and Modeling</li>



<li>year: Elective courses, project-based applications and internships</li>
</ol>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can also expand your education options by getting information about <a href="http://roadtostudy.com" data-type="link" data-id="roadtostudy.com">Özyeğin University Faculty of Business Administration</a> and <a href="http://roadtostudy.com" data-type="link" data-id="roadtostudy.com">Özyeğin University Business Administration Department</a>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition, if you would like to review the detailed curriculum and course content of Özyeğin University&#8217;s Faculty of Business Administration, you can also check out <a class="" href="https://www.ozyegin.edu.tr/pdfviewer/isletme-2023-2024.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Faculty of Business Administration 2023-2024 Brochure</a>.</p>


