<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="campus-life-and-social-facilities">Campus Life and Social Facilities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Located on the Istanbul-Çekmeköy campus, <strong>Özyeğin University Department of Economics</strong> offers students an educational environment in touch with nature. Thanks to the campus&#8217; large green areas and modern dormitories, students have a pleasant educational experience.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="hospitality">Hospitality:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Single/double dormitory rooms</li>



<li>Modern workspaces and social communal areas</li>



<li>Hostels on campus; safe and easy to reach</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="social-opportunities">Social Opportunities:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Finance and business clubs, sports clubs, art events</li>



<li>Service to the city center</li>



<li>Library, cafe, gym and recreation areas</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="student-clubs">Student Clubs:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Business Club</li>



