<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="apostille-procedures-abroad-and-admission-to-turkey">Apostille Procedures Abroad and Admission to Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">What if you want to have your student certificate apostilled outside Turkey? In this case, both the consulate and the authorized institution in the host country come into play. If the document issued in a foreign country is to be used in Turkey, it must bear an apostille annotation.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-is-the-apostille-process-performed">How is the Apostille Process Performed?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">First, the original and a photocopy of the document are submitted to the competent authority (e.g. the governor&#8217;s office or the ministry of justice of that country) for apostille. The document is examined by the competent authority and after the authenticity of the document is confirmed, an apostille annotation is added. The apostille annotation is usually attached to the back of the document or as a separate page.</p>



