<li>A photocopy of the document</li>



<li>Copy of ID or passport</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can start the apostille process by applying to the District Governorship or Governorship with these documents. The apostille is usually delivered the same day or the next day. Thanks to the apostille, your student document gains legal validity in countries that are parties to the Hague Conference.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-results-of-the-apostille-process">The Results of the Apostille Process</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">After the apostille process is completed, the student document officially becomes internationally valid. In other words, a student certificate obtained in Turkey is considered legal and official in other Hague Conference member countries. Using this document, you can proceed smoothly in many areas such as visa applications, university applications or scholarship procedures.</p>


