<iframe loading="lazy" title="Bir Bölüm Üç Açı - Uluslararası Finans Mezun &amp; Öğrenci" width="720" height="405" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FzLg40d9-o4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University is rapidly rising as one of Turkey&#8217;s leading foundation universities. The International Finance program stands out especially for international students with its location close to Istanbul&#8217;s business world, global education opportunities and contemporary campus life.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-international-finance-and-why-is-it-so-popular">What is international finance and why is it so popular?</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="change-the-rules-of-the-game-in-the-global-economy">Change the Rules of the Game in the Global Economy</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International Finance is much more than just dealing with numbers. Covering topics such as foreign exchange markets, global investment strategies, risk management and sustainable finance, this field teaches you to read the world economically. Today, companies and investors know no boundaries; if you want to be part of this system, you must have a solid financial foundation.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="fields-where-graduates-can-work">Fields where graduates can work</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Career options for International Finance graduates are truly vast. Here are some popular areas:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>International banking</li>



<li>Investment advisory</li>



<li>Financial technology (fintech) companies</li>



<li>Risk management and audit</li>



<li>Financial departments of multinational companies</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is also common to advance academically through master&#8217;s and MBA programs.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="fees-and-admission-requirements-for-international-students">Fees and Admission Requirements for International Students</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="training-fee">Training Fee</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As of 2025, the annual fee for international students at Özyeğin University&#8217;s International Finance program is <strong>20,000 USD</strong>. </p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="application-requirements-and-required-documents">Application Requirements and Required Documents</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The following documents are usually requested for application:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>High school diploma and transcript </li>



<li>English proficiency certificate (TOEFL, IELTS or Özyeğin&#8217;s own exam)</li>



<li>Passport photocopy</li>



<li>Letter of intent</li>



<li>Online application form</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="english-proficiency-and-other-requirements">English Proficiency and Other Requirements</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Since the program is entirely in English, language proficiency is of great importance. TOEFL IBT usually requires at least 80 points and IELTS requires at least 6.5. If you do not have these documents, you can join the university&#8217;s preparatory program.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-is-finance-education-at-ozyegin-university">How is Finance Education at Ozyegin University?</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="an-english-supported-4-year-program">An English-Supported, 4-Year Program</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University&#8217;s International Finance program is offered in 100% English. This not only prepares you academically for world standards but also enables you to communicate easily in the global business world. The duration of the program is 4 years (8 semesters). You have the opportunity to take elective courses in many different fields during your education.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-does-aacsb-accreditation-mean">What does AACSB Accreditation Mean?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University is currently in the <a href="https://admissions.ozyegin.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>AACSB accreditation process</strong></a>. This is a prestigious quality approval given only to elite business schools around the world. If the process is completed, being a graduate of Özyeğin will mean having an internationally recognized diploma. This puts you one step ahead.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="general-structure-of-the-curriculum-and-credit-distribution">General Structure of the Curriculum and Credit Distribution</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In order to graduate from the Department of Finance, students must complete 240 ECTS credits. This obligation is grouped as follows:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th><strong>Course Category</strong></th><th><strong>Number of Courses</strong></th><th><strong>Total ECTS Credits</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Core and Compulsory Courses</td><td>34</td><td>176</td></tr><tr><td>In-Program Electives</td><td>4</td><td>24</td></tr><tr><td>In-Faculty Electives</td><td>2</td><td>12</td></tr><tr><td>Out-of-Faculty Electives</td><td>2</td><td>12</td></tr><tr><td>Free Electives</td><td>2</td><td>12</td></tr><tr><td>Internship / Certificate</td><td>2</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Total</strong></td><td><strong>46</strong></td><td><strong>240</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This structure not only provides you with basic finance knowledge, but also allows you to enrich yourself with different disciplines.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="studying-in-istanbul-being-a-student-at-the-heart-of-finance">Studying in Istanbul: Being a Student at the Heart of Finance</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="proximity-to-financial-centers">Proximity to Financial Centers</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Istanbul is Turkey&#8217;s economic brain. Özyeğin University is positioned right in the center of this dynamism. Thanks to its proximity to the Istanbul Financial Center, students have the chance to learn finance not only in theory but also in practice. Most students get various internship opportunities outside the classroom and meet the sector before graduation.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This is a big advantage, especially for international students, because Istanbul is home to the majority of Turkey&#8217;s international companies. This puts you in the same ecosystem as multinational banks, investment firms and fintech startups.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="life-for-international-students-in-the-city">Life for International Students in the City</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Living in Istanbul means witnessing a fascinating cultural heritage while enjoying all the amenities of metropolitan life. Özyeğin University is located within easy reach of the city center. This means you can go for a walk on the Bosphorus on the weekend or have a coffee with your friends in Karaköy.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Because Istanbul is home to many international students, it is easy to create a social circle. With the international orientation programs and events organized by the university, you can quickly get used to the city and school.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="campus-life-and-social-facilities">Campus Life and Social Facilities</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="dormitories-clubs-and-social-activities">Dormitories, Clubs and Social Activities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University campus attracts attention with its modern architecture and its structure intertwined with nature. There are comfortable dormitory options on campus for international students. The rooms are usually for 2 people and are equipped with high-speed internet, a workspace and a shared kitchen.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The university has over 70 student clubs, including finance, entrepreneurship, dance and theater. Whether you want to boost your CV or join a club for pure fun, all kinds of social experiences await you here.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="internship-and-certificate-opportunities">Internship and Certificate Opportunities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As part of the program, students are required to complete an internship worth 2 credits. They also have the chance to participate in certificate programs in some semesters. Thanks to Özyeğin&#8217;s strong ties with the business world, many students find internship opportunities at banks, investment advisory firms and even companies abroad.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These experiences make it incredibly easy to find a job after graduation. Indeed, even adding an internship at Özyeğin to your CV can sometimes open a door.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University&#8217;s finance program offers a strong learning environment not only through its course content, but also through the modern campus facilities of the <strong><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-universitesi-isletme-fakultesi/" data-type="post" data-id="3384">Faculty of Business Administration and other departments</a></strong>.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="start-today-be-a-global-leader-tomorrow">Start Today, Be a Global Leader Tomorrow!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to take your place in the world of finance, don&#8217;t wait. Özyeğin University&#8217;s International Finance program offers you a fully equipped start both academically and practically. Moreover, with its English-language education, international accreditation process and location in the heart of Istanbul, this experience will make you stand out not only in Turkey but also in the world.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="reach-the-right-guidance-with-road-to-study">Reach the Right Guidance with Road to Study</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The application process can be complicated, but you are not alone. At <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a>, we offer guidance on the right documents, application steps and scholarship opportunities. Let&#8217;s complete your application together and take you step by step to the university of your dreams.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Now is the time to apply. The world of finance is waiting for you.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-07-23T12:37:57Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:47:16Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/ozyegin-universitesi-international-finance.webp","alt":"Ozyegin University International Finance","title":"ozyegin-universitesi-international-finance"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ozyegin-university-international-finance';
