<p class="wp-block-paragraph">MIS professionals manage a company&#8217;s information systems and integrate all business functions such as general management, finance, marketing and human resources. This means that graduates are not just IT professionals, but professionals who develop strategies, build decision support systems and create data-driven solutions.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-this-department-is-one-of-the-professions-of-the-future">Why This Department is One of the Professions of the Future?</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Digitalization is no longer an option, but a necessity. Every technological development, from artificial intelligence to big data, increases the need for experts in this field. In particular, technologists with managerial vision are much more preferred in the global business world.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


