<iframe loading="lazy" title="Bir Bölüm Üç Açı - Uluslararası İlişkiler Mezun &amp; Öğrenci" width="720" height="405" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sG4kKJOB-xg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>


<div style="height:38px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Özyeğin University Faculty of Social Sciences, which includes departments such as International Relations, Psychology, and Anthropology, offers students not only a theoretical but also a practical model of education. The campus is equipped with modern classrooms, interactive seminars and research centers.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="international-relations-position-and-academic-structure">International Relations Position and Academic Structure</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The International Relations program focuses on topics such as global diplomacy, foreign policy, and international security. Thanks to OzU&#8217;s strategic location in Istanbul, students have direct contact with various consulates, international organizations and foreign NGOs. This increases internship opportunities and facilitates the creation of a professional network.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="interdisciplinary-relations-with-psychology-and-anthropology">Interdisciplinary Relations with Psychology and Anthropology</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International Relations is not limited to political issues. It is also integrated with other branches of social sciences such as psychology and anthropology. In this way, students gain a more comprehensive perspective on culture, human behavior and social structure.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are curious, you can take a look at <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-universitesi-psikoloji-bolumu/" data-type="post" data-id="3768">Ozyeğin University Psychology Department Overview</a> and get to know the general structure of the faculty better.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-are-the-advantages-of-studying-international-relations">What are the Advantages of Studying International Relations?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International Relations is not just an academic field; it is also a lifestyle that provides a global vision. At Özyeğin University, this program goes beyond theoretical knowledge. Students have the chance to communicate with global actors, learn negotiation techniques and participate in real diplomacy simulations.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="english-education-and-academic-staff">English Education and Academic Staff</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The program is conducted entirely in English. Most of the lecturers are names who have studied abroad and whose publications are included in academic journals. In this way, students can experience not only book knowledge but also field experience in the classroom environment.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="international-student-profile-and-cultural-diversity">International Student Profile and Cultural Diversity</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Currently, there are many international students in the department. Being in the same classroom with students from every continent is a natural way to develop cultural awareness. OzU not only supports but also encourages this diversity. The international cultural festivals held every year on campus are enriched by the events organized by student clubs.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="tuition-fee-and-scholarship-opportunities-2025-2026">Tuition Fee and Scholarship Opportunities (2025-2026)</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For students who want an international university experience, OzU offers both quality education and scholarship advantages. As of the 2025-2026 academic year, the annual tuition fee for the Department of International Relations is <strong>22,000 USD</strong>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="updated-education-fee-table-and-discount-rates">Updated Education Fee Table and Discount Rates</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University eases the burden of many students with its scholarship opportunities. Fees for students receiving scholarships vary as follows:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th><strong>Scholarship Rate</strong></th>
<th><strong>Annual Fee (USD)</strong></th>
</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>50%</td>
