<h3 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">What happens if the family residence permit expires?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><p class="wp-block-paragraph" data-start="1614" data-end="1855">If the family residence permit expires, e.g. if the parent&#8217;s permit expires or if the family unit is no longer united, the child can switch to a short-term residence permit if the conditions are met. This ensures that the education process is not interrupted.</p></p>



